ity-metadata.json`\n\nThe new test exercises the public `MoreCallCredentials.from(ServiceAccountCredentials)` path with an unscoped service account, then applies request metadata and verifies a JWT bearer authorization header is produced. This reaches the remaining `JwtHelper` reflection call sites.\n\nTests were not run, per instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_07c319aa788287460169f88c1a8c0c819ea0e84940a6b88aaf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1040, "output": 1262, "cacheRead": 40448, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 42750, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777896459040, "responseId": "resp_07c319aa788287460169f88c0b9160819e81d7617c0a000c0b"}}
